data.meta_description: Zip code 14572 in Wayland, NY local info. 14572 has 5,228 residents in 2010-2014, ranked #714 in New York zip codes. Also 14572 schools, income, races, weather, environment and other info / rankings.
data.text:
14572 zip code is located in west New York. 14572 zip code is between the Steuben, Livingston county. 14572 zip code has 74.73 square miles of land area and 0.32 square miles of water area. As of 2010-2014, the total 14572 zip code population is 5,228, which has shrunk 1.02% since 2000. The population growth rate is lower than the state average rate of 3.26% and is much lower than the national average rate of 11.61%. 14572 zip code median household income is $41,047 in 2010-2014 and has has shrunk by 2.83% since 2000. The income growth rate is much lower than the state average rate of 35.25% and is much lower than the national average rate of 27.36%. 14572 zip code median house value is $91,700 in 2010-2014 and has shrunk by -38.10% since 2000. The house value growth rate is much lower than the state average rate of 90.79% and is lower than the national average rate of 46.91%. As a reference, the national Consumer Price Index (CPI) inflation rate for the same period is 26.63%. On average, the public school district that covers 14572 zip code is better than the state average in quality. The 14572 zip code area code is 585.
